title: NA Speaker, Deputy Speaker tender resignations
content:
ISLAMABAD, Apr 10 (APP):Speaker National Assembly Asad Qaiser and Deputy Speaker Qasim Khan Suri on Saturday tendered resignations from their respective offices.According to the Assembly Secretariat, both the Speaker and Deputy Speaker have tendered resignations. Elections for the slots of Speaker and Deputy Speaker would be held before the election of new leader of the House, it further said.
